Package org.obapanel.jedis.cache.simple

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CacheLoader
    Used to give a cache read-through capabilities or when loading data into a cache from external sources (like a database)
    CacheWriter
    Used to give a cache write-through capabilities or when storing data into a cache, to also store in external sources (like a database)
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CacheIterator
    Iterator that travels by all pairs of key-values of the cache.
    CacheKeyIterator
    Iterator that travels by all keys of the cache.
    SimpleCache
    A cache is a Map-like data structure that provides temporary storage of application data.
